\id 3JN
\h 3 JON
\toc1 3 Jon
\toc2 3 Jon
\toc3 3 Jon
\mt1 3 Jon
\c 1
\s1 Aan Yeya
\p 
\v 1 Aya, sios nẽ mudur ado,
\p turau oboiyou Gaius, aya ĩ nigin momoi anĩ bun, wau laa fedig, ĩ bun pas enei atotof.
\p 
\v 2 Turau oboiyou, ogon malãkanon biya ibodok gen, õ boũ biya ibod ken, ereb ereb ganan õ nigin biya ilauf nigin, aya kosẽ auf.
\v 3 Turau tar tunĩ disi fen, õ momoi anĩ biya bagai dõ wo fen, momoi anĩ bun toku uyõdig anĩ dirokana di, aya fatuk bagai wau al fen.
\v 4 Aya gereu tar momoi anĩ bun diyõdig karĩya anim, wau al fiya ereb ereb ganan wal fiya anĩ ifanadig.
\s1 Negur Nẽ Kabĩ Tamo Kulatun Fediya
\p 
\v 5 Turau oboiyou, õ, turada tar idi, õ bun yaũ tamo anidi nigin el wo, biya ago wedidig.
\v 6 Idi ogon waũ laa fiya nigin sios dirokenẽdin. Õ idi tobonunã Negur orof kilei sur wediyouf are, õ biya ago wouf.
\v 7 Idi Odug yana nigin, haiden bun tamal isennẽya taka to dale fen, dilen.
\v 8 Anĩ nigin, ada, momoi anĩ nigin weim kabĩ talouf nigin, tamo age fediya tasennẽdiyouf bagai.
\p 
\v 9 Aya sios bun pas atoton, anĩ ere, Diotrefes uyulil ibodõya nigin wau laa fedig, ĩ nemã od to karĩ yedig.
\v 10 Anĩ nigin, aya asiyouf sain bun, aya ĩ ereb age fef, amã nigin dumen od sane bagai irõdig anĩ yaor afouf. Anĩ dogol sã, ĩ turada tar yalediya nigin itoron. Ĩ idi turada tar yaleya nigin orodif anidig katũ feid fen, idi sios bun tamal yalelnẽdin.
\p 
\v 11 Turau oboiyou, ereb sane anĩ to madẽ wo, ereb biya anĩ madẽ wouf. Aib taka ereb biya age fef, ĩ Negur bun tamal. Aib taka ereb sane age fef, ĩ Negur to ilen.
\v 12 Demetrius ĩ nigin, ganan biya wogõ dedig, momoi anĩ ĩ yogog age fedig. Amãg ĩ nigin biya wogõ maudig, age mafe di, ã keleĩ, nemã wogõ are momoi.
\s1 Idikeleya Nẽ Aanya
\p 
\v 13 Aya õ bun itotoya nigin musei ado, anĩ ere, aya pepa ado ink nem itotoya nigin to orouf.
\v 14 Aya kaisã ileyõya nigin wau irok, age afe fen, abob nawa tail fen, wogõ tauf.
\p 
\v 15 Wau inosiya õ bun ibodõf. Turada tar ein, nedi aanya sur difef. Turada tar an mugu mugu yeneid nem aan wediyouf. 
